Fashion Affair - July 2013

English | True PDF | 178 pages | 70 MB

Fashion Affair Magazine is an International publication designed to bring you the best in existing, new and up & coming fashion around the world. There are many designers you never see or hear about because of the insurmountable price tags associated with most publications. Fashion Affair Magazine seeks to change all of that.
